OL,3,CFirefighter 'failed by LFB' who took
OL,4,Cown life 'not victim of discrimination'
OL,6,FAn investigation into the death of a
OL,7,Fyoung black firefighter who took his
OL,8,Fown life has found no evidence of
OL,9,Fdirect discrimination, bullying or
OL,10,Fharassment by his colleagues.
OL,12,FJaden Francois-Esprit, 21, a
OL,13,Ffirefighter at Wembley fire station
OL,14,Fdied at his home in Wapping, east
OL,15,FLondon, in late August 2020.
