OL,3,CFirefighter 'failed by LFB' who took
OL,4,Cown life 'not victim of discrimination'
OL,6,FHis family feared he had been bullied
OL,7,Fby London Fire Brigade (LFB)
OL,8,Fcolleagues because of his race,
OL,9,Fhowever, an independent external
OL,10,Freview, published on Tuesday, found no
OL,11,Fevidence this was the case.
OL,13,FHowever, Andy Roe, the LFB
OL,14,Fcommissioner, said the organisation
OL,15,Fhad "failed" Mr Francois-Esprit.
