OL,3,CFirefighter 'failed by LFB' who took
OL,4,Cown life 'not victim of discrimination'
OL,6,FAllegations claiming Mr Francois-
OL,7,FEsprit was unfairly singled out,
OL,8,Fteased about Caribbean food in his
OL,9,Fpacked lunches and exposed to a toxic
OL,10,Fworking environment, were not upheld
OL,11,Fin the report, which took a year to
OL,12,Fcomplete.
OL,14,FThe report found the dyslexic junior
OL,15,Ffirefighter was not provided with a
OL,16,Flocker when he started and his bed,
OL,17,Fused to rest on night shifts, was in a
OL,18,Fpoor state - but, neither of these
OL,19,Finstances were unique to him.
