OL,3,CFirefighter 'failed by LFB' who took
OL,4,Cown life 'not victim of discrimination'
OL,6,FReport investigators added Mr Francois-
OL,7,FEsprit had concerns other firefighters
OL,8,Fwould roll their eyes when he made tea
OL,9,Fand ridicule him if he spilt any.
OL,11,FInvestigators said in the report: "It
OL,12,Fis possible that a cumulative lack of
OL,13,Fconfidence, not least when speaking to
OL,14,Fan audience, Jaden's working
OL,15,Fconditions with an initial lack of
OL,16,Flocker provision, the inadequacy of
OL,17,Fbeds and consequent sleep issues, and
OL,18,Fthe 'tradition' of making tea, could
OL,19,Fhave had a disproportionate effect on
OL,20,FJaden due to his neurodiversity.
