OL,6,F"Most of these issues were working
OL,7,Fconditions for all firefighters
OL,8,Fserving at the fire station and were
OL,9,Fnot designed or intended to cause
OL,10,FJaden any detriment.
OL,12,F"It is understandable that a man aged
OL,13,F20 might find the working conditions
OL,14,Fto be not what he had expected.
