OL,6,F"The impact of the pandemic ` the
OL,7,Funcertainty of his progression, the
OL,8,Fimmediate change to social norms and
OL,9,Fresulting sense of individual
OL,10,Fisolation, for example ` is likely
OL,11,Falso to have negatively affected
OL,12,FJaden's wellbeing.
OL,14,F"It is also possible that what
OL,15,Fexperienced firefighters saw as 'team
OL,16,Fbuilding' or development activities
OL,17,Fwere not perceived as such by someone
OL,18,Fwho was neurodiverse."
