OL,3,CFirefighter 'failed by LFB' who took
OL,4,Cown life 'not victim of discrimination'
OL,6,FTuesday's report comes after an
OL,7,Findependent culture review of LFB, led
OL,8,Fby Nazir Afzal, a former chief crown
OL,9,Fprosecutor for the North West, and
OL,10,Freleased in November 2022, found the
OL,11,Forganisation to be institutionally
OL,12,Fmisogynist and racist in the wake of
OL,13,FMr Francois-Esprit's death.
OL,15,FAt an inquest into Mr Francois-
OL,16,FEsprit's death at King's Cross
OL,17,FCoroner's Court in February 2021, his
OL,18,Fmother Linda Francois said her son was
OL,19,Fbeing "unfavourably singled out
OL,20,Fbecause he's an ethnic minority".
