OL,3,CFirefighter 'failed by LFB' who took
OL,4,Cown life 'not victim of discrimination'
OL,6,FShe said he "hated" working at Wembley
OL,7,FFire Station, and had told her his
OL,8,F"crew manager" was bullying him.
OL,10,FShe added her son was concerned about
OL,11,Fnot receiving learning support from
OL,12,FLFB with his dyslexia, and that he
OL,13,Ffelt "isolated, bored and unfulfilled"
OL,14,Fat work.
OL,16,FThe cause of his death was recorded as
OL,17,Fsuspension.
