OL,3,CFirefighter 'failed by LFB' who took
OL,4,Cown life 'not victim of discrimination'
OL,6,FSpeaking at City Hall on Tuesday, fire
OL,7,Fcommissioner Andy Roe said: "None of
OL,8,Fthe allegations against the
OL,9,Frespondents, those who were complained
OL,10,Fabout, were formally upheld.
OL,12,F"However, I need to be clear as
OL,13,Fcommissioner, that while those
OL,14,Ffindings are clear and I fully accept
OL,15,Fwhat in the end has been a
OL,16,Fcomprehensive indepednent externally-
OL,17,Fled process - it it still my personal
OL,18,Fview that we let Jaden down as an
OL,19,Forganisation.
OL,26,@oD@]OU
