OL,3,CFirefighter 'failed by LFB' who took
OL,4,Cown life 'not victim of discrimination'
OL,6,F"I believe we failed him through poor
OL,7,Fprocesses and the leadership culture,
OL,8,Fas well as long-established
OL,9,Forganisational approaches that didn't
OL,10,Fwork."
OL,12,FHe added: "I want to be clear (the
OL,13,Ffindings) do not mean Jaden's personal
OL,14,Flived experience at the brigade was
OL,15,Fnot a factor in his untimely death.
