OL,4,Cown life 'not victim of discrimination'
OL,6,F"I personally believe we failed Jaden
OL,7,Fas an organisation because the
OL,8,Freport's findings do indicate failings
OL,9,Fin our day-to-day protocols,
OL,10,Fapproaches and systems as they were at
OL,11,Fthat time."
OL,13,FMr Roe said there were problems with
OL,14,Fthe brigade's "reliance" on long-
OL,15,Fstanding systems and its approach to
OL,16,Fhuman resources at the time.
